      "source": [
        "# **Project 5: Part-of-Speech (POS) Tagging**\n",
        "\n",
        "## Objective\n",
        "\n",
        "In this project, you'll learn how to identify the **grammatical role** of each word in a sentence using **Part-of-Speech (POS) Tagging**.\n",
        "\n",
        "For example:\n",
        "\n",
        "> **Sentence:**\n",
        ">\n",
        "> *The Ukrainian president condemned the Russian attack.*\n",
        "\n",
        "| Word      | POS Tag | Meaning           |\n",
        "| --------- | ------- | ----------------- |\n",
        "| The       | DT      | Determiner        |\n",
        "| Ukrainian | JJ      | Adjective         |\n",
        "| president | NN      | Noun              |\n",
        "| condemned | VBD     | Verb (Past Tense) |\n",
        "| the       | DT      | Determiner        |\n",
        "| Russian   | JJ      | Adjective         |\n",
        "| attack    | NN      | Noun              |"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "34f0db80"
      },
      "source": [
        "---"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "a5710962"
      },
      "source": [
        "# Why POS Tagging?\n",
        "\n",
        "POS tagging is useful in:\n",
        "\n",
        "* Information Extraction\n",
        "* Named Entity Recognition (NER)\n",
        "* Machine Translation\n",
        "* Question Answering\n",
        "* Text Summarization\n",
        "* Search Engines\n",
        "* Chatbots\n",
        "* Feature Engineering for Machine Learning"
      ]
    },
